March 27th, 2018 tgagg
1. RELEASE.NOTES file is created
2. M ecsMotorRecordApp/Db/ecsMotorControl.sch  
   + Added $(dev) macro to all symbols
   + Added frame 
   + handshake input name changed from: handshake to hskinp to be consistent
      with handshake output (status) called hskstat
   + Added counter (using calc) for each processing
   + Connected cascade FLNK for outputs
   + Inserted ao records between longin and ecsMoRec so links are properly
      connected to vals.
3. M configure/CONFIG_SITE
 As we are using it as SoftIOC right now, exclude other architectures to get
