August 1st, 2018 pgx/tgagg

1. Debugging vars ready for use when needed:
M       ecsMotorRecordApp/src/ecsMotorRecord.dbd

2. Timeouts adjusted: 
M       ecsMotorRecordApp/src/ecsMotorRecordDefs.h

3. Updated the bit combining routines:
M       ecsMotorRecordApp/src/ecsMotorRecord.c
  - Under ecsMotorRecordScanTask setHandshakeBits(pmr, pmr->hinp); was replaced
  with new routine: updateInputBits(pmr);
  - Some printfs are cleaned and enabled to allow greater diagnostics if needed
   during the first operation runs.
  - updateInputBits: Update changes in the handshake input bits into the 
  handshake output. With this corrections we do not relay anymore on occasional 
  delays on the PLC side with updating the bits status.
  - writingState: Correct wrong timeout name.
  
4. Added a new engineering routine to test bit combining functions.
A         ecsMotorRecordApp/src/testHs.c


